--- a/Documentation/arm64/silicon-errata.rst
+++ b/Documentation/arm64/silicon-errata.rst
@@ -107,6 +107,8 @@ stable kernels.
 +----------------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------------------+
 | Cavium         | ThunderX2 SMMUv3| #126            | N/A                         |
 +----------------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------------------+
+| Cavium         | ThunderX2 Core  | #219            | CAVIUM_TX2_ERRATUM_219      |
